{"tid":1131693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最後一次 你問我答（秒回）","createTime":"2019-04-29T22:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T00:40:08.000Z","uid":112439,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b069b730c1d7db57c5411b55e29626f6a80708f4","tid":1131693,"uid":112439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T22:55:02.000Z","msg":"一直以嚟，我每日都有上連登。<br />\n由於我打中文唔快，所以無成日留言／開post。<br />\n不過，今日係我最後一次登入同埋上連登。<br />\n<br />\n而家個account係我同個ex兩年前一齊開，而且都係我同佢最後一個連接。 （我唔覺得佢再有上連登啦)<br />\n今日係分手之後既第15個月，頭先唸住stalk下你，唔經唔覺又喊左半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我終於係social media都block晒大家，今日最後一次開post，大家有無野想知道。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 人地過得好好，ex個新對象都好好，只不過係時候要逼自己放低。"},{"pid":"72dd5cc059696f8ecd69cf2d111221742b29ac11","tid":1131693,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:13:04.000Z","msg":"雖然冇睇你篇野<br />\n不過我都好同情你遭遇<br />\n請問你屋企廚房幾大呢？"},{"pid":"b0f1429eef68b70796f0a7320251deff2e62bc2b","tid":1131693,"uid":112439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72dd5cc059696f8ecd69cf2d111221742b29ac11","tid":1131693,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:13:04.000Z","msg":"雖然冇睇你篇野<br />\n不過我都好同情你遭遇<br />\n請問你屋企廚房幾大呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"我笑左出聲哈哈<br />\n屋企係開方式廚房連住個廳，所以煮完野食通常都好大陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bb9e4d7d8bbe9e37081c27c411a8db992f4e0a","tid":1131693,"uid":161741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:42:52.000Z","msg":"摺埋啦好嗎"},{"pid":"6964ff3dca3998690c4a497e3c59714aa9e6d5c6","tid":1131693,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:46:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ca7bbfbedc6eb79a77ce08bd9d9a503eaed9fa3","tid":1131693,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"叫春就叫春 乜撚嘢你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" clas